This app uses VES and Kiwi mobile visualization framework.  Visit
the developer's guide at http://vtk.org/Wiki/VES for download and
build instructions.

To build this app, edit tools.sh and set the paths correctly for your
environment.  Set the ANDROID_NDK environment variable to the location
of your Android NDK installation, and then run the bash scripts in order:

./configure_cmake.sh
./configure_ant.sh
./compile.sh
./install.sh

Make sure your device is connected before running install.sh.
